OL,6,FSpeaking to the BBC, the Chancellor
OL,7,Fsaid she values public service workers
OL,8,Fand "people won't have long to wait
OL,9,Ffor a decision".
OL,11,F"There is a cost to not settling, a
OL,12,Fcost of further industrial action, and
OL,13,Fa cost in terms of the challenge we
OL,14,Fface recruiting," she told Sunday With
OL,15,FLaura Kuenssberg, stressing her
OL,16,Fspending rules were "non-negotiable".
OL,18,F"We will do it in a proper way and
OL,19,Fmake sure the sums add up," she added.
