OL,6,FDiscussing public sector pay on Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning, Reeves accused Conservative
OL,8,Fformer ministers of "running away"
OL,9,Ffrom making a decision.
OL,11,FShe singled out former education
OL,12,Fsecretary Gillian Keegan, saying the
OL,13,Fpay review body's recommendations for
OL,14,Fteachers had been on her desk for
OL,15,F"months".
OL,17,F"She didn't do anything about it. She
OL,18,Fdidn't publish it, she didn't say how
OL,19,Fshe was going to respond to it," Ms
OL,20,FReeves said.
