OL,6,F"They called an election, they didn't
OL,7,Fmake the tough decisions, they ran
OL,8,Faway from them and it's now up to us
OL,9,Fto fix it and to pick up the pieces."
OL,11,FMinisters have repeatedly blamed their
OL,12,Fpredecessors for leaving them with the
OL,13,Fworst fiscal inheritance since the
OL,14,FSecond World War.
OL,16,FBut former chancellor Jeremy Hunt told
OL,17,FSunday With Laura Kuenssberg this was
OL,18,F"absolute nonsense" and designed to
OL,19,Flay the groundwork for tax rises.
