OL,6,FHe said: "I was looking until a couple
OL,7,Fof weeks ago at the same numbers that
OL,8,FRachel Reeves is now looking at.
OL,10,F"It's very clear that if you are
OL,11,Fprepared to show restraint on public
OL,12,Fsector pay, as we did last year, if
OL,13,Fyou're prepared to be ambitious on
OL,14,Fpublic sector productivity, as I was
OL,15,Fin the budget, and you're prepared to
OL,16,Fdo welfare reform, which was glaringly
OL,17,Fabsent from the King's Speech ` if you
OL,18,Fdo those three things it's perfectly
OL,19,Fpossible to balance the books in a way
OL,20,Fthat means taxes don't have to rise.
